        <briefdescription>
<para>This function runs a self-test on the driver and hardware device. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This self test writes reset value into safety check register and read backs the same. If mismatch offers, returns the failure.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_x_rtc_psu" kindref="compound">XRtcPsu</ref> instance</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if the test was successful</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para></para></simplesect>
This function can hang if the hardware is not functioning properly. </para>        </detaileddescription>
